title: The Garden Kafe at The Yoga Barn
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Raw, Western, Buffet, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe tucked away from the main street. Offers choices in vegetarian, vegan, and raw food. Has smoothies, fresh juices, raw desserts, and a menu for detox and Ayurvedic rejuvenation. Rice field view dining overlooking the terraced lawn and amphitheater of The Yoga Barn. Free Wi-Fi and newspaper.
